<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Oracle on Bruno Rozendo</title><link>https://brunorozendo.com/tags/oracle.html</link><description>Recent content in Oracle on Bruno Rozendo</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>pt-BR</language><copyright>Code released under the Apache 2.0 license.</copyright><lastBuildDate>Mon, 18 Apr 2016 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://brunorozendo.com/tags/oracle/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Criar Database Oracle 11g</title><link>https://brunorozendo.com/post/criar-database-oracle.html</link><pubDate>Mon, 18 Apr 2016 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://brunorozendo.com/post/criar-database-oracle.html</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Por curiosidade instalei um banco oracle numa maquina ubuntu e para minha surpresa criar uma database e bem mais complexo.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Exemplo válidos em mysql e postgre, mas que não funciona no oracle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;create&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;database&lt;/span&gt; teste;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Eis aqui a mágica, precisamos criar um &lt;code&gt;TABLESPACE&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;DATAFILE&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;USER&lt;/code&gt; e dar as permissões (&lt;code&gt;GRANT&lt;/code&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;O produto final:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="terminal"&gt;
 &lt;div class="header"&gt;
 &lt;img src="https://brunorozendo.com//images/layouts/shortcodes/terminal.png" alt=""&gt;
 &lt;div class="title"&gt;Terminal&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;bruno@ubuntu:~$: sqlplus / as sysdba
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;SQL*Plus: Release 11.2.0.2.0 Production on Qui Jul &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;27&lt;/span&gt; 11:39:36 &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2017&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Copyright &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;c&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; 1982, 2011, Oracle. All rights reserved.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;SQL&amp;gt; connect / as sysdba
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Conectado a uma instância inativa.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;SQL&amp;gt; CREATE TABLESPACE &amp;lt;database&amp;gt; DATAFILE &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/u01/app/oracle/oradata/XE/&amp;lt;database&amp;gt;.dbf&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; SIZE 100m AUTOEXTEND ON NEXT 100m EXTENT MANAGEMENT LOCAL AUTOALLOCATE;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Tablespace criado.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;SQL&amp;gt; CREATE USER &amp;lt;database&amp;gt; IDENTIFIED BY &amp;lt;database&amp;gt; DEFAULT TABLESPACE &amp;lt;database&amp;gt; TEMPORARY TABLESPACE temp;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Usuário criado.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;SQL&amp;gt; grant all privileges to &amp;lt;database&amp;gt; identified by &amp;lt;database&amp;gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Concessão bem-sucedida.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;SQL&amp;gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Feito! agora basta conecatar com sua ferramenta de preferência.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>